message:
Hi Everyone,
We have a meetup for designers. We'll talk, have fun and get to know each other. It's gonna be on Saturday March 19th 12:00 pm in Starbucks Tivoli. For any questions reach out to me. Hope to see you there. Spread the word and bring your friends with you :)
We can also talk about Sketch Vs Photoshop. New prototyping tools like principle or Framer. Workflows and etc... I'm too excited that I can talk for days :D
